{"tid":422821,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［Rainbow6】香港隊出戰悉尼前最後一戰","createTime":"2017-10-03T11:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T13:50:06.000Z","uid":35990,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d839b9dcfc2583f17bf2c1c3bab5d029aecb57e6","tid":422821,"uid":35990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:37:18.000Z","msg":"其實大部分人都話，SEA Region入面嘅兩強同其他隊實力相差好大<br />\n即係今晚會上演嘅就係真正會打到難分難解嘅精彩比賽！<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/193547_bfd0722315ac4652f0ffd0c4b7e1ea26.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F193547_bfd0722315ac4652f0ffd0c4b7e1ea26.png&h=af579c00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Pro League SEA 最後一日】<br />\n話就話上星期就決定咗香港隊uM同新加玻隊Tyde將會出戰悉尼<br />\n但係今日先係今季Pro League SEA嘅最後比賽日<br />\n因為終極兩強都係要決一高下爭取首名出線！<br />\n<br />\n香港時間八點鐘，嚟Devils台睇官方廣東話直播！<br />\n直播連結：<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/devilsgaminghk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fdevilsgaminghk%2F&d=0h42LnngE9u5w8NSj%2FaLYsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=bb6d4d41\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/devilsgaminghk/</a><br />\n<br />\n（今次啲過場畫面應會順返少少唔會咁樣衰的了）"},{"pid":"b8ba41f69421c3354c6d0db06045fe0d732d36cf","tid":422821,"uid":35990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6802fa13373b71fe07cded61c625d1c8b173db","tid":422821,"uid":35990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495e24499775b9abd45be633d13d812d279f7c04","tid":422821,"uid":35990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee025c698d5f53